The,Audio,API,from,Vodafone,is,part,of,a,suite,of,JavaScript,based,widget,APIs,that,provide,mobile,web,applications,access,to,the,underlying,hardware,The,Audio,API,lets,developers,play,common,audio,formats,right,in,the,mobile,browser,The,API,provides,a,basic,player,interface,including,play,pause,resume,and,stop,functions,allows,repeat,play,supports,playing,of,local,and,remote,files,i,e,audio,streaming